nodes.text: We estimate we have four to five months before the vault runs out of water. We need that chip!
You have two months, maybe less, before the vault runs out of water.  We need that chip!
If we didn't have to do this, I'd never ask. And if you don't do this, I don't know who else can. Help us. You're our only . . . chance, I guess.
You have three months to retrieve the chip before the vault runs out  of water.
If you need help, come back here. Obviously, we'll do whatever we can. But we don't have a lot of time.  Be safe, find that chip, and get back here.
There's a picture on your PIP to help you identify it.

We marked your map with the location of another Vault. Not a bad place to start, I think. Then again, what the heck do I know about the outside? I . . . look. Y' You know you're important to me and to . . . I-I really . . . just be safe, OK?
